Author: JohnPierson
Title: [ANN] [Contractium.io] One of the top ICOs with Product-Ready-Launch, ICO starts
Body: Thanks for the link. To be honest, I have seen this part and actually don’t get it. For me both the detention and examples don’t answer on the question what problem is solved by the tokenization.  CTU is a must-have element, a fuel, - the value of contract - , for signing the commercial smart contract on Contractium application. CTU is a form of payment as well as contract, made by contracter and contractee (customer and business) when they proceed a deal; place an order; book a service online/offline. CTU is the incentive ensuring to make the operational procedure between 02 parties, on blockchain based Contratium, trustful completed and one of the the both can earn extra added-value CTU back with rewards policy of CTU network.  The definition tells that the token is must have element of the system. But what for is the system, I cannot get the real world problem. Asking because sometimes startups trying to solve an imagined virtual problem. Does the team did proper customer development?

On behalf of Contractium Team, I would like to make an announcement today, on Saturday 7th July 2018, that:  */ Contractium is organizing the ICO (Initial Coin Offering) event officially, starting with Private Sales for ICO-Investors as well as Cryptocurrency-Investors. /*  As you may know that, there were many scammers with ICOs, so we kept pending and pending our ICO event for several months to develop the MVPs (Minimum Viable Products) as planned. The 02 MVPs are:  1.The Smart-Contract-App https://mvp.contractium.io/ [close-alpha-testing-version] Help end-users deploy (commercial) smart contracts easily, securely, trustless to work together (ex. in the freelance industry) without technical knowledge & skills.  2.The Tokenize-App https://tokenize.contractium.io/ [alpha-testing-version] Help business-users deploy smart contract, issue tokens on Ethereum as well as on the other blockchains...  With the tokenize-application, we help everyone (who want to do cryptocurrency-related-business) issue their own tokens without technical knowledge & skills.  We, Contractium, bring the equal opportunities to everyone in this era of blockchain & cryptocurrency industry.  We, Contractium, have mission and vision to open the new gate of “privatization of money” when blockchain will take over the world of tokenize-economics in the near future.  I, personally, believe that the “privatization of money” with blockchain & cryptocurrency, will re-establish, reset & reform the world economy in the next 10 years.  To keep developing what we are developing, the applications, that help everyone issue tokenize-money, we need to organize this ICO event to raise funding.  And we need you, the cryptocurrency-investors as well as the ICO-investors.
